flowchart TD
    A[User interaction<br/>Keyboard or pointer] -->|Trigger: src/frontend/src/lib/components/QueryForm.tsx<br/>QueryForm onSubmit| B[App.handleRun<br/>src/frontend/src/App.tsx]
    A -->|Trigger: src/frontend/src/App.tsx<br/>Load/Vectorize form onSubmit -> handleLoadSubmit| A1[App.handleLoadSubmit]
